{"tid":712230,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(請教大阪酒店)","createTime":"2018-06-22T02:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T12:40:19.000Z","uid":156354,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd75ed96b4fba7a76711b5fd09244296451dc81","tid":712230,"uid":156354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"下列大阪三間酒店，有冇巴絲住過？？？<br />\n<br />\n邊間坐地鐵去，阪、神、奈、環球影城，會方便d。已網上訂了三間，第一次去大阪，7月中去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1)Hotel WBF ARTSTAY Namba<br />\n    WBF ART STAY 難波飯店<br />\n<br />\n(2)Hotel Sunroute Osaka Namba<br />\n     難波燦路都大酒店<br />\n<br />\n(3)Nest Hotel Osaka Shinsaibashi<br />\n     大阪心齋橋NEST酒店<br />\n<br />\n三間價錢差不多，原本想住 1，貪佢夠新，又文青，但好似地鐵站冇咁方便，驚第一次兩條傻西蕩失路，請教各位巴絲。"},{"pid":"36e457463d895ea8fd1a16f425b91350b7374732","tid":712230,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"sunroute"},{"pid":"3f26ad27e0054ca5c258be2f5e5abb2688334e07","tid":712230,"uid":156354,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"36e457463d895ea8fd1a16f425b91350b7374732","tid":712230,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"sunroute"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"請問房間冷氣熱不熱？和厠所干淨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n(sunoute見網上評語說冷氣不夠)"},{"pid":"abfb2b026e17ff3c0262cf4eb120fd9eb9e10bc7","tid":712230,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3f26ad27e0054ca5c258be2f5e5abb2688334e07","tid":712230,"uid":156354,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"36e457463d895ea8fd1a16f425b91350b7374732","tid":712230,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"sunroute"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"請問房間冷氣熱不熱？和厠所干淨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n(sunoute見網上評語說冷氣不夠)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"干乜撚"},{"pid":"2becf1e82fe8cd82be219c1dcd39509ad9c13f82","tid":712230,"uid":116836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"